{"tid":1428741,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［轉台］跪求巴絲幫手填問卷，順便籌錢俾612 支援基金","createTime":"2019-08-07T10:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T20:01:13.000Z","uid":284565,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ab241c5fde1c8ded5669c3453c5fc14ab25e90c1","tid":1428741,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:51:09.000Z","msg":"係呢種時候，身為P 牌仔咁同大家講都唔係太好意思......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小妹最近有份工係大學做問卷調查，需要270 位UGC funded 嘅undergrad（<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">有去過exchange 的話更加需要，有個sample size</span></strong></span>，唔可以太多太少）填份問卷。<br />\n<br />\n每填一份問卷，我人工會多25蚊，呢筆錢全部會用作612 人道支援基金捐款。link 係下面，希望大家幫幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n個 project 越快完，我越快可以confirm 到人工。我到時捐左錢會放入數紙上黎（270*25 = 6750）。數字雖小，但大家用5分鐘填份問卷就可以幫到小小，唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖則話理論上可以亂填，不過呢份問卷調查嘅結果對大學生未來exchange 都可能有多少影響，所以設左問題要大家嘅學生電郵（唔會send 野俾你）。請各位巴絲唔好亂填，或者填幾份，data 會作廢。<br />\n<br />\n問卷link： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FyoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6&d=%2BDaDB54%2FKEfuO7Vsi8VjQ1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=4bb3b67f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/yoZUDnYsL9wTj54b6</a><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"7985a5044bd8b09109ebfb123955ed32daadbe75","tid":1428741,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"006a430780015c35dae5f5d2e25689acf4f87e86","tid":1428741,"uid":284565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"755271e8c69f70a7ff9d9d4795ebf7c591ba298e","t